{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't until about-- I don't remember exactly-- five years, six, seven years ago when I was in Israel that a-- a daughter-- a granddaughter for the woman who was saved-- went to a magazine that is very well known in Israel.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say like Life Magazine in here-- and divulged the whole story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was splashed up all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every detail that I was just recounting here was all told there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not directly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I had contact with him that he was my, so to say, my boss.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was the one who saw me every day going like in the main camp for-- but I was never beaten by him, or--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't-- I-- other than, maybe, slap somebody a little, I never saw him perform any bad deeds.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing-- not other-- any other that I knew that he was doing because she intervened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, somebody got into serious trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember, in camp you get in serious trouble for-- for little things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like somebody is caught that he takes from the packages that he's supposed to sort.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You find a ring in your pocket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- that's-- that's almost death penalty, because they-- we were all warned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, you take food-- you're not supposed to take food, either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they'll catch you with a sweater because it's warm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's not going to kill you for that, either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But to take what they're really searching for is gold, diamonds, money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was a federal offense.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, that was big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if the SS in that camp felt like pulling his gun out to shoot you, he wasn't giving any accounting to anybody for that.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
